{"tid":565101,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老母想睇老豆電話 老豆即刻熄機","createTime":"2018-02-18T16:20:45.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-20T03:43:09.000Z","uid":26823,"like":2,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"a5829e56a477aca43bbd656c70b8a8a8e5ddfcf6","tid":565101,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:20:45.000Z","msg":"頭先老豆飲大左 老母係咁嘈佢 叫佢沖涼<br />\n老豆唔聽 想撖電話 老母見到就想睇佢撖乜 然後老豆即刻熄機<br />\n<br />\n老豆六十歲 做啲十年如一日既粗工 冇娛樂 冇朋友<br />\n基本上冇乜人會搵佢 但呢排每星期都會有日唔返屋企食<br />\n有時紅日又會話返工 同同事食飯 手機又間唔中有 message既鈴聲響<br />\n我本身就有啲懷疑 但我老母係好天真嗰啲 佢世界係冇出軌叫雞嗰啲嘢 好信老豆<br />\n<br />\n而家老豆訓左 睇唔睇佢電話好？"},{"pid":"027ccf03fd3a1d683c33b48448bad82fabeb4fe7","tid":565101,"uid":73909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"同we7 雞 chat 緊"},{"pid":"4a8d45320d2e8306cc1a9423e424cb65818e2fd9","tid":565101,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"027ccf03fd3a1d683c33b48448bad82fabeb4fe7","tid":565101,"uid":73909,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:21:39.000Z","msg":"同we7 雞 chat 緊"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:22:29.000Z","msg":"我都懷疑係 睇唔睇好"},{"pid":"ee3429e7364b32dbdf6efbf63a4ff73c279cc53b","tid":565101,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:22:30.000Z","msg":"你都有曬結論, 仲駛咩睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6b95966457f1f8a4bd4c63274ed4ad75d9123f38","tid":565101,"uid":26823,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"ee3429e7364b32dbdf6efbf63a4ff73c279cc53b","tid":565101,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:22:30.000Z","msg":"你都有曬結論, 仲駛咩睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:22:49.000Z","msg":"有懷疑啫 冇證實"},{"pid":"564dcdfb11263bd7cc990523c59011314c374420","tid":565101,"uid":74171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-18T16:23:08.000Z","msg":"可能睇緊長輩J圖"},